00:37:04,719 --> 00:37:07,439
The floor here
is made of special material.

824
00:37:07,879 --> 00:37:08,760
It is extremely tough.

825
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:10,080
This person would have to weigh

826
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:12,800
