843
00:37:47,840 --> 00:37:49,399
That's not the only thing I'm good at.

844
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:53,479
You are like a treasure

845
00:37:54,239 --> 00:37:55,520
to me.

846
00:37:59,080 --> 00:38:00,399
Even so,

847
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:01,879
