864
00:38:36,120 --> 00:38:36,719
That's right.

865
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,479
16 taels weigh one jin.

866
00:38:39,879 --> 00:38:40,719
10,000 Silver leaves

867
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:42,840
weigh a total of 625 jin.

868
