00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:38,959
Congratulations, Sir.

886
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:43,120
The Sacred Jade Moon can only suppress
the blood curse temporarily.

887
00:40:44,080 --> 00:40:45,360
If I want to remove it completely,

888
00:40:46,080 --> 00:40:47,840
